result.name: Green River Restaurant

reviews.text:
This is a neighborhood restaurant. I had breakfast here today consisting of a fish cutlet and coffee.

Unfortunately the waiters are very arrogant, impolite, rude and very unhelpful. They really could not care less about their customers and have no idea what customer service is and what is required.

The food is very standard in taste. Prices are moderate. Coffee was mediocre which is very surprising for such cafes as their tea and coffees are usually what they excel in. Not the case here.
Breadfast untill noon good for brunch

大眾化小炒，味道服務都還可以。
